title: Ep. 174 "Holding Who Down?"
description:
This week we revisit an old conversation to see where we stand now. How long are you holding someone down, if ever, how long will you stick out rough patches in relationships? Maybe we've changed, maybe we haven't. Leave a comment and answer the questions with us!

Also we have bonus content available on Patreon! Visit www.patreon.com/cocktales to sign up, $3 pledges and higher get access to bonus content. Your support is greatly appreciated!

Contact us for all inquiries/collaboration requests at cocktales.atl@gmail.com and submit your advice emails to askcocktales@gmail.com only.
